_sText:
This is my first map. The map consists of several floors of glass, each becoming increasingly difficult to break. There are explosives barrels, cars and other items, so try and kill your opponent in an imaginative way ;) 

There is a secret chamber with an AK47, Deagle and grenade in it. 

The big slabs of white tinted glass can be broken, however they are difficult to break. 

Hope you enjoy it, and I hope to be playing it on servers soon.
